                <bold>Examples of solutions, good practices and concrete experiences</bold>
            </p>
            <list list-type="bullet">
                <list-item>
                    <p>CITYLOOPS has developed food demand management models in Porto (Portugal) to minimise food waste generation.</p>
                </list-item>
                <list-item>
                    <p>In the HOOP &#x201c;Lighthouse&#x201d; Kuopio (Finland), the waste management company J&#x00e4;tekukko encourages households to compost to reduce biowaste production. The unpublished report by the 
                        <xref ref-type="bibr" rid="ref-20">HOOP project (2022)</xref> of Kuopio urban metabolism reveals that they generate approximately 40% less biowaste than the average of the other HOOP Lighthouse Cities and Regions.</p>
                </list-item>
